# Walkthrough: Student Profile — Real Data & Functional UI

## Summary
Replaced all dummy/placeholder content on the student profile page with live data. Created a server-side annotation persistence layer so book highlights and notes are available across the app.

## Changes Made

### New Files
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [create_annotations_table.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/database/migrations/2026_03_02_100000_create_annotations_table.php) | Migration for [annotations](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/app/Models/User.php#71-75) table |
| [Annotation.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/app/Models/Annotation.php) | Annotation model (belongsTo User, Book, BookChapter) |
| [settings_partial.blade.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/resources/views/frontend/student/settings_partial.blade.php) | Settings form partial loaded via AJAX into profile Settings tab |

### Modified Files
| File | Changes |
|------|---------|
| [User.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/app/Models/User.php) | Added [annotations()](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/app/Models/User.php#71-75) hasMany relationship |
| [StudentController.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/app/Http/Controllers/StudentController.php) | Updated [profile()](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/app/Http/Controllers/StudentController.php#251-259) to pass annotation data; added [storeAnnotation()](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/app/Http/Controllers/StudentController.php#270-288), [getAnnotations()](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/app/Http/Controllers/StudentController.php#289-298), [deleteAnnotation()](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/app/Http/Controllers/StudentController.php#299-305), [settingsContent()](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/app/Http/Controllers/StudentController.php#265-269) |
