| [profile.blade.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/resources/views/frontend/student/profile.blade.php) | Full rewrite — see detail below |
| [read.blade.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/resources/views/frontend/library/read.blade.php) | `saveAnnotation()` syncs to server; [deleteAnnotation()](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/app/Http/Controllers/StudentController.php#299-305) deletes from server |

### Profile View Fixes
- **"Years Member" → "Member Since"**: Shows `Auth::user()->created_at->format('M Y')` (e.g. "Feb 2026")
- **Reflections count**: Now shows `$annotationCount` from real DB data
- **My Notes**: Real annotations with book title, timestamp, highlighted text, and anchor link to reader
- **Tabs**: JavaScript tab switching between Spiritual Journey / My Notes / Settings
- **Settings tab**: Loads via AJAX (`fetch('/settings/content')`) on first click
- **Buttons**: "Edit Profile" → opens Settings tab, "View All" → opens Notes tab, "Update Preferences" → opens Settings tab, "Go to Library" → links to library

## Validation
- ✅ Migration ran: [annotations](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dbim/core/app/Models/User.php#71-75) table created
- ✅ All 4 new routes verified via `php artisan route:list`
- 🔲 Manual browser test recommended
